1958;;The Perfect Furlough;;American;;Blake Edwards;;Tony Curtis, Janet Leigh, Linda Cristal;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Perfect_Furlough;;Corporal Paul Hodges, after a long period in an isolated Arctic base, wins a lottery and gets to Paris, France, on a three weeks leave. There he will be under psychiatrist lieutenant Vicky Loren's control.